-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20784,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/30\/blessed-istighfar-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":15694,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: Blessed is one who seeks forgiveness often","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Busr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessed is he who finds many prayers for forgiveness in his record.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3818 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0628\u0646 \u0628\u0633\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0637\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e\u0649 \u0644\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34760,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/dhikr-angels-announce\/","url_meta":{"origin":15694,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Angels declare forgiveness for circles of remembrance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Hanzalah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit together to remember Allah Almighty and stand to leave until a heavenly caller says to them: Stand and your sins are forgiven by Allah! Your bad deeds have been replaced with good\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18467,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/09\/dua-parents-children-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15694,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: Parents rewarded for their good children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty will raise the status of His righteous servants in Paradise, and they will say: O Lord, what is this? Allah will say: This is your child seeking forgiveness for you.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38556,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/26\/stubborn-istighfar\/","url_meta":{"origin":15694,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: Not a sinner if sincerely repenting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 26, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne is not a stubborn sinner if he sincerely seeks forgiveness from Allah, even if he were to do it seventy times in a day.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3559 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Muflih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/d